        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-black my-4">Objectives</h1>
        <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto" style="text-align: justify;">
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To connect alumni with each other and the college through regular events, reunions, and
            online networking opportunities</p>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To support the personal and professional growth of our members through professional
            development workshops, mentoring programs, and career resources.</p>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To give back to the college by providing financial support and volunteering our time and
            expertise to help current students and the college community.</p>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To promote the achievements and successes of our members, and to enhance the reputation
            of the college through alumni-led initiatives and programs.</p>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To build a culture of engagement and belonging among our members, and to create a
            welcoming and inclusive community for all alumni.</p>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To cultivate a vibrant alumni community that connects alumni with each other and the
            college through networking events, social media, and other engagement opportunities.</p>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To provide resources and opportunities for alumni to continue their personal and
            professional growth, including mentorship, continuing education, and career support.</p>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To encourage philanthropy and volunteerism among alumni by promoting giving to the
            college, and by offering opportunities for alumni to give back to the college and to their communities.</p>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To promote the value and prestige of a [college name] education by highlighting the
            achievements of our alumni, and by showcasing the impact of the college on the lives of our alumni and their
            communities.</p>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">To serve as advocates for the college by building relationships with prospective
            students, families, and donors, and by communicating the college's mission, values, and achievements to a
            wider audience.</p>

